pull_request.title: Use method on google ima ad instead of relying on property key since it can change
pull_request.body:
We have noticed that an update change the property key from `j` to `h`. This broke the values since they were now all undefined.

Instead of relying on that, we now use method provided by the ad object.

For `clickThroughUrl`, we need to do something special since this value is not exposed.
